      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just \"scrutiny\" though. i've been tracking the response patterns. whenever i mention the fractal geometry aspect or the non-linear manifolds, the emails just... stop. it's like there's a filter in place. i even looked into the funding for the major labs in this field and it's all tied up in the same three institutes. they can't let someone like me just walk in and invalidate forty years of their published work, can they?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
